<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Verified - Welcome to Malinta Connect</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #1e40af;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #059669;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .details {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #1e40af;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
        }
        .value {
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        .success-note {
            background-color: #ecfdf5;
            border-left: 4px solid #059669;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .features-list {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://malinta-connect.vercel.app/images/malinta_logo.jpg" alt="Malinta Connect Logo" class="logo">
            <h1 style="color: #1e40af; margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">Account Verified!</h1>
            <div class="status-badge">VERIFIED</div>
        </div>

        <p>Dear <strong><%= residentName %></strong>,</p>

        <div class="success-note">
            <strong>✓ Congratulations!</strong> Your account has been successfully verified and approved.
        </div>

        <p>We're pleased to inform you that your Malinta Connect account has been verified. You now have full access to all services and features available on our platform.</p>

        <div class="details">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;">Account Details</h3>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="label">Name:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= residentName %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="label">Email:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= email %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="label">Verification Date:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= verificationDate %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="label">Status:</span>
                <span class="value"><strong style="color: #059669;">Verified</strong></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="features-list">
            <strong>You can now access:</strong><br>
            • Request barangay certificates<br>
            • Book appointments with officials<br>
            • File blotter reports<br>
            • View announcements and events<br>
            • Update your profile information
        </div>

        <% if (notes && notes.trim() !== '') { %>
        <div style="background-color: #eff6ff; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <strong>Note from Administrator:</strong><br>
            <%= notes %>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <p>Start exploring the services available to you by visiting our website.</p>

        <p><strong>Need Help?</strong></p>
        <p>If you have any questions about using the platform or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>

        <ul style="color: #6b7280;">
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +63 912 345 6789</li>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> barangaymalintalosbanos@gmail.com</li>
            <li><strong>Office Hours:</strong> Monday - Friday, 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for registering with Malinta Connect. We're here to serve you better.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>